quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  101,1,The calamity
  101,2,what is the calamity
  101,3,And what shall apprise thee of the calamity
  101,4,A day wherein mankind shall be like scattered moths
  101,5,and the mountains shall be like carded wool
  101,6,As for one whose scales are heavy
  101,7,he shall enjoy a life contenting
  101,8,And as for one whose scales are light
  101,9,an abyss shall be his mother
  101,10,And what shall apprise thee of her
  101,11,It is a raging fire